{"tid":1594180,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《蘋果》懸紅50萬　追緝襲擊女記者兇徒","createTime":"2019-09-25T12:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T14:46:27.000Z","uid":99478,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"865d91245b191a5b64c6ea9c4117c0a8235cefdf","tid":1594180,"uid":99478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:21:48.000Z","msg":"《蘋果日報》女記者昨日遭4名兇徒襲擊，全城憤怒，《蘋果》發出嚴正聲明，強烈譴責兇徒暴行，並懸紅50萬元，發動全城緝兇，希望市民提供消息，協助將兇徒繩之於法。<br />\n<br />\n全文如下︰<br />\n2019年9月24日（星期二）晚上約8時15分，《蘋果日報》一名女記者在秀茂坪順天邨天權樓地下大快活，遭4名穿黑衣黑褲的蒙面男子襲擊，部份行兇者當時頭戴黃色頭盔。<br />\n<br />\n本報現懸紅港幣50萬元正。任何公眾人士若有此案的消息、或知悉兇徒的身份或下落，請盡速聯絡本報。凡在案發起半年內，提供資料致使兇徒繩之於法者（即被檢控並在本港法院就此案作出答辯），將可全數或按比例分配賞格。<br />\n<br />\n聯絡本報可致電24小時報料熱線2929 0000、手機短訊6383 6568或電郵adnews@appledaily.com<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUPDCWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUPDCWT.jpg&h=13274710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190925/60083332?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2d60KvcCU9qy2bxdT1m7ymz7Piqvmw9fpajrTqCuzf6gemsejP8Yp0tt0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190925%2F60083332%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2d60KvcCU9qy2bxdT1m7ymz7Piqvmw9fpajrTqCuzf6gemsejP8Yp0tt0&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=2c31f3c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190925%2F60083332%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2d60KvcCU9qy2bxdT1m7ymz7Piqvmw9fpajrTqCuzf6gemsejP8Yp0tt0&h=19e609d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190925/60083332?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2d60KvcCU9qy2bxdT1m7ymz7Piqvmw9fpajrTqCuzf6gemsejP8Yp0tt0</a>"},{"pid":"cc4119e99845b8941fe452d0ee96a4a44cef1498","tid":1594180,"uid":275314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:23:21.000Z","msg":"去附近既狗屋搵會唔會易啲搵到兇手"},{"pid":"09e3b273ff946db0faac037200a645c68714f23f","tid":1594180,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:27:07.000Z","msg":"老豆搵仔"},{"pid":"d117e01c224dbb407c403547e7396093ba99db9f","tid":1594180,"uid":175208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9455d12b80c9525752666d9db26d7285eb1da338","tid":1594180,"uid":321593,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:46:27.000Z","msg":"幫手推呀，滴土共無法無天搵黑社會伏擊記者。"}]}